<div align="center"><span class="textbold_orange">AMPK Phosphorylation Status Screening Service (Code: pAMPK Service)</span><br /><br /></div>

<span class="textbold_orange">Summary</span><br />
Using our <a href="/AMPK-Phosphorylation-Assay-Kit" target="_blank">EnzyFluo&trade; AMPK Phosphorylation Assay Kit</a>, we screen for modulators that increase or decrease AMPK phosphorylation status in cells. We measure the AMPK phosphorylation kinetics, EC50, and IC50 of cells treated with modulators. Testing can be run on a wide variety of cell lines.
